{"tid":1387371,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"預計事態發展","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:48:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:43:50.000Z","uid":226562,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4124b517907d40de24ff8cf77b858fdf0030fcf1","tid":1387371,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:48:46.000Z","msg":"利申 9估<br />\n以下進程係以 6 月起嘅急速事態發展速度作估算<br />\n同埋係假設政府完全不作實質回應<br />\n關於政府唔同反應對事態發展嘅效果可睇最底註解<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">日期</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">和理非行動</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">勇武派行動</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">警方／政府行動</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">6.9</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">百萬人大遊行</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">小規模衝擊立法會</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">警棍、胡椒噴霧</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">6.12</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">幾萬人圍立法會</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">磚頭、鐵馬衝擊</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">橡膠子彈、催淚彈</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">6.16</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">二百萬人大遊行</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">無</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">無影</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">6月尾</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">包圍警察總部、特首辦</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">雞蛋油漆攻擊</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">不反抗企圖挽回民意</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">7月頭</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">地區遊行</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">開始反抗打狗</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">集會完結前強力鎮壓，甚至打入室內</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">7.21</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">民陣大遊行</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">搞中聯辦</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">重新開槍，嘗試用黑社會勢力製造白色恐怖調停事件</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">7.27,7.28</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">元朗／港島遊行</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">開始對催淚彈有免疫，開始玩火</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">企圖以不批出不反對通知書壓制遊行，升級武力鎮壓，大規模行動，警隊開始進入瘋狂狀態</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">7.29</span>____國務院發表言論鞏固警察執法權，非必要不出解放軍，希望盡快回復秩序<br />\n------以下為9估------<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">8.5</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">開始大規模罷工癱瘓政府運作、交通、以至經濟</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">冇</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">冇</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">8月頭</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">分區集會削弱警力</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">開始玩 popo go</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">出動水炮車但係示威者 be water 無功而還</span><br />\n------政府回應訴求死線，一旦越過呢條線，香港局勢將無法挽回，只有中央收回本港再慢慢變成新彊市同埋送給英美／獨立兩條路<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">8月中</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">社會及經濟癱瘓</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">開始捉小精靈入精靈球</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">開始內亂</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">8月尾到9月中</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">經濟癱瘓，分區集會，接近無政府狀態</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">開始有小精靈被捉之後唔知去咗邊，並獲得小精靈技能</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">嘗試輯兇，但因無方向而失敗，開始因黑色恐怖而內亂，唔敢返工</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">9月尾</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">無政府狀態</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">獲得一定技能</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">警察瓦解</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">10.1 前後</span>____<span style=\"color: blue;\">進入政府設施搶奪物資，清算非本土人士 e.g. 新移民</span>____<span style=\"color: brown;\">正式宣布香港獨立</span>____<span style=\"color: pink;\">解放軍／外國勢力正式介入</span><br />\n之後 who knows<br />\n<br />\n政府唔同回應嘅後果：<br />\n全面回應五大訴求：市民接受，警察持槍暴動，解放軍進場<br />\n五大訴求但特赦示威者及警察，獨立調查委員會非刑事清算警察（雙方最好結果）：廣泛市民接受，部分勇武派可能有零星集會，警察內部分化接受清算<br />\n成立獨立調查委員會，總極撤回：和理非可能減少一部分，勇武派依然存在，整個進程拖慢半個月至個半月<br />\n<br />\n利申真係 9 up<br />\n中左嘅話可以頒個諾貝爾獎比我"},{"pid":"10960387763c5c869bb459451aa3b931b160f123","tid":1387371,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"諾貝爾狗噏獎?"},{"pid":"eaefd454837c3361e1fc05661147e5b634f13c55","tid":1387371,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"10960387763c5c869bb459451aa3b931b160f123","tid":1387371,"uid":16061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:52:06.000Z","msg":"諾貝爾狗噏獎?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:54:50.000Z","msg":"講笑啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb154b3aea4f236826ed607a2288e9d9ff82921","tid":1387371,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:57:28.000Z","msg":"有咁順利就好，我估開學後熱情冷卻，不了了之，遊行不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da929692c83d08f48aae076a16de25fba3ae897","tid":1387371,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcb154b3aea4f236826ed607a2288e9d9ff82921","tid":1387371,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:57:28.000Z","msg":"有咁順利就好，我估開學後熱情冷卻，不了了之，遊行不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:20:01.000Z","msg":"有感按照而家速度，9月前會發展到全面癱瘓，學校唔開，冇車返學"},{"pid":"211935a652d0d3568de005db22d76d4dccb899b5","tid":1387371,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"9 up"},{"pid":"37a4f2492ff2d5152bea7407de0b87b4a0e54aa0","tid":1387371,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:43:50.000Z","msg":"似乎預言成真了"}]}